data.description: 55 plus gated community and you own your land.  This home offers a large updated kitchen, laminate and tile flooring throughout the main areas of the home. large laundry room with a ton of storage through out the home that includes a walk in closet.   Off of the bedroom is an additional room that can be used as an office, den or craft/sewing room.  On the side of the house is a nice enclosed latus patio to enjoy your morning coffee or entertain family and friends.  Great community with a heated pool/spa, tennis, pickleball, basketball, shuffleboard, billiards, putting green, common areas and clubhouse with many amenities and community events. Community is near, golfing, hiking, shopping, restaurants, hospitals and the US 60 and Red Mountains 202 for easy access around the valley,
